*Mala* je šetala po gradu. (She was walking around the city.)

*Male* su ribe u akvarijumu. (The fish in the aquarium are small.)

*Malom* bebom je bila potrebna pažnja. (The little baby needed attention.)

*Maloj* je pričala priču pred spavanje. (She told a story to the little one before sleeping.)

*Malu* je pohvalio zbog dobrog rada. (He praised the little one for a good job.)